description: This file defines a React component called SearchResults that displays search results, including loading states, error messages, and result items. It uses TypeScript types for component props and result normalization.

methods.name: typeBadge
methods.description: Creates a badge span element with styling based on the 'type' of the search result.

methods.name: SearchResults
methods.description: Main React component that renders search results, handling various UI states such as loading, error, and empty results. It renders a list of result items with details.
